!! Please read links below first
Create full db backup
innobackupex --rsync /path/to/BACKUP-DIR/

prepare full backup
innobackupex --apply-log /path/to/BACKUP-DIR

restore full backup
innobackupex --copy-back /path/to/BACKUP-DIR

Links: http://www.percona.com/doc/percona-xtrabackup/2.1/innobackupex/innobackupex_script.html